# =============================================================================
# UPES-ECS .gitignore
# Rule of thumb: never commit secrets, real rosters/PII, captured emergency
# audio, live runtime state, or build artifacts. Ship *.example templates
# instead so a fresh clone knows the schema.
# =============================================================================

# --- Secrets / credential stores -------------------------------------------
secrets/
*.secret
*.secrets
*.pem
*.key
*_key
**/id_rsa*
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# --- Real personal data (PII) — keep local, ship *.example instead ----------
# Rosters, user provisioning, and family links contain real names / SAP IDs.
provisioning/pilot-users.csv
provisioning/linphone/users.csv
provisioning/user-languages.csv
provisioning/family/families.csv
*.filled.csv
provisioning/*.filled.csv
# Console roster + live runtime state
Console/directory.json
Console/status.json
# Asterisk account file — contains REAL SIP secrets (its own header forbids
# committing it). Managed via Add-UpesUser.ps1; ship pjsip_accounts.example.conf.
deploy/asterisk/pjsip_accounts.conf
# Local working notes (rosters, demo coordination, credentials references)
Notes/

# --- Captured emergency data (must stay on the server, per retention policy)-
*.wav
recordings/
voicemail/
Console/recordings/
Console/logs/
# Generated Piper TTS voice prompts are NOT committed (keeps clones lightweight,
# no Git LFS). Regenerate them at setup with scripts/gen-*-prompts.* (see
# deploy/asterisk/sounds/README.md). The sounds/ folder keeps only its README.

# --- Removed feature: Flutter mobile app (archived in tag mobile-app-archive)
app/

# --- Python ----------------------------------------------------------------
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
.venv/
venv/
.pytest_cache/

# --- Build / packaging artifacts (large; rebuild on demand) -----------------
dist/
build/
*.exe
*.qcow2
*.iso
*.apk
extensions_custom.conf.bak-*

# --- MkDocs ----------------------------------------------------------------
site/

# --- Runtime / health output -----------------------------------------------
health.txt
*.log

# --- OS / editor noise ------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
/NUL
.idea/
*.swp
